{"tid":1419071,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【戰後檢討】我宣布反送中民間記者會","createTime":"2019-08-05T23:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T03:03:21.000Z","uid":240968,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"18aed20d63cd4148fd85ecbcbce5f6e41c66246c","tid":1419071,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:32:57.000Z","msg":"我有個好痴線嘅諗法，<br />\n有D 長，但唔好走著，<br />\n因為除左佔領機場渣政府春袋以外，<br />\n成場運動和理非 / 勇武缺一不可，<br />\n而黎個方法係可以改變和理非勇武分化局面，<br />\n對勇武黎講係尤其重要！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">風險雖大，但只要做到第一次，大家壯到膽，就可以破解淋病 <br />\n每日跨部門記招/ 黑狗記招政府 既洗腦分化陰招，<br />\n挽留和理非甚至提升我地既民意支持。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n原理係：<br />\n<br />\n1）當港共約時間安排記招，<br />\n2）馬上吹雞搵d 講野OK/議論能力比較強既手足外（最少10個以上，和理非勇武需合作無間） <br />\n+/- 一兩個立法會議員/組織代表去記招出面睇live（如果可以），<br />\n3）完左後挽留班記者朋友，善用時機，馬上開民間記招。<br />\n<br />\n禁既話，<br />\n最重要既效果係<br />\n-   政府無辦法控制資訊唱衰我地，一面倒講我地做到有幾衰（除某紅媒），從而抗分化、抗洗腦。<br />\n-  文宣不是和理非既專利，近日發生左好多事，我明白各手足都好嬲，但勇武既行為係紅媒/藍絲渲染之下開始被部分和理非/淺黃（部分為三毛所扮演）割蓆，黎個係鐵一般既事實。催淚彈入民居，係可以令部分街坊勇武，但不停破壞狗屋/BBQ 係會令和理非/淺黃 對勇武卻步。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民間記招，勇武係可以向市民講清楚自己既底線，同時可以進行公民再教育/ 輸出革命</span></span></strong>。所以民間記者會，勇武既參與係為整場運動落定心丸！！勇武一定要黎！！！！（完記招後既行動我無建議）<br />\n-   請善用記招既號召力。當你係地鐵站禁辛苦先airdrop 到一張圖出去，或者留係同溫層分享資訊，或者你同旁邊食飯嘅藍絲阿伯理論。只要黎個民間記招講一兩三句，聽到既人講緊既係幾百萬人，係包埋 鍾意聽收音機成日屌7你既司機，同鍾意睇cctvb既廢老藍絲啊！！民間記招可以宣傳將來行動/方向，又唔洗被瘋狂藍絲費老搞到爆血管，仲可以黎支持君亞bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同各大媒體記者手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，性價比同佔領機場睇齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n-  我地都可以做好形象大使，（例如：手足來自各行各業，上黎講會令運動增加民意授權 / 我地身無屎，唔會似班狗官調頭走避問題，禮貌加分）<br />\n<br />\n有人擔心時間準備不足，講完一定有好多位被人，<br />\n開記招講錯野分分鐘仲大獲，不如另約時間在開記招。<br />\n<br />\n但我強調點解一定要馬上開民間記招，有以下兩個優點，<br />\n第一，唔洗另約傳媒同地點。<br />\n第二（好重要），媒體播新聞次序係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">跟單新聞既重要性/時間性</span></span></strong>，<br />\n港共記招後民間記招，新聞次序就好大機會港共記招接住落民間記招，<br />\n個效果就好似係辯論比賽，你屌我馬上博，<br />\n禁就唔會令對家偷換概念，合理化我地做既所有野。<br />\n再者，佢依家五大訴求一個都無應承，你淨係Jer住佢黎個point，<br />\nelab下再講行動點動搖到政府，其實真係唔洗好勁議論能力都講到<br />\n<br />\n淋病話會每日搵隻狗同大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，又開跨部門記者會，想同大家探討開民間記者會既難易：<br />\n針對黑狗記招既民間記者會：較易<br />\n點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為班毅進狗已經詞窮，一味話我地暴力份子 ，<br />\n所以我地只要輸出同大眾講黑警先係真正既暴力份子，<br />\n強調佢地清場/濫暴黑材料就得，黎三日大把料，夠講2個鐘，<br />\n加上大家發夢都對警隊認知/通例認識增加唔小， 連 prepare 都唔洗，<br />\n<br />\n跨部門記招：較難<br />\n-  手足未必明白各部門運作，回應上黎會困難<br />\n-  解決方法：<br />\n 1）開記者會就要答曬佢最maincore既野，講行動既原則，避輕就重<br />\n 2）問TG 開民間記者會既TG gp<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n講著緊多先，我已經兩日無訓，但堅持打埋落去，<br />\n第一係因為我覺得work，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同時，我唔想個400個義士做condom，<br />\n要對得起佢地，<br />\n就係唔好令整個革命付之流水。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家比下意見啦，我訓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不分化，不割蓆</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林病月娥 屌你老母"},{"pid":"6716e5efa7978b35081478340461bc5479bb0dcd","tid":1419071,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:33:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c1371e16613bf35d776ea7490cfba617ffff14f","tid":1419071,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:33:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6723b524bc4d5384912d82ae19331f4d17e7d1c","tid":1419071,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:34:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5722ebac5a010da131bdb36042ed59e7eec80d1e","tid":1419071,"uid":240968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:35:12.000Z","msg":"打左半晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113d0976dea63635d3c4b1baaebe652b1b6939e0","tid":1419071,"uid":80303,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:36:30.000Z","msg":"各位記唔記得大家出嚟係為咗啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地咁辛苦 咁頻密咁出嚟<br />\n唔係為咗cosplay 著曬full gear 然後坐喺到un un 腳㩒電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦都唔係為咗食煙 食彈 唔走 等被人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加唔係為咗要禁止他人發聲 街坊講咗少少嘢唔啱聽就屌人 打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地出嚟嘅初心 <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">係為咗對抗哩個腐敗嘅政權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係為咗追求自由民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有為咗彰顯公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n我發現 有啲人好熱心咁出嚟 但就忘記咗出嚟嘅初衷⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一 禁止他人影相的人</span></strong><br />\n點解我地一開始唔比人影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為驚黑警認得出你係邊個 然後拉你<br />\n<br />\n不過香港係無肖像權嘅 每個人都有影相嘅自由<br />\n如果因為人地影相而屌人<br />\n咁同吉野家因為一句「撕紙狗」而炒人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係剝奪咗一啲與生俱來嘅自由<br />\n如果唔想被人影到 應該要遮好自己啲特徵<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>然後客氣咁講「記得唔好影人地嘅大頭啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n而唔係「咪影相啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">二 打深藍街坊的人</span></strong><br />\n好明顯 深藍街坊 係反對我地集會、遊行嘅<br />\n就好似我地反對港共政權一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我地因為佢地講嘢唔啱聽而打人<br />\n咁同黑警向和平集會嘅人放煙又咩分別呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪一樣都係打壓緊言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實佢地話你 你圍住佢唱生日歌 或者話返佢咪夠囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果佢地唔係主動出手 做咩要傷害佢地呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三 阻止手足去制服黑社會的人</span></strong><br />\n我地出嚟 係因為官、警、商、黑勾結啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑社會係無性㗎 佢地唔會同你講道理㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地根本就有曬準備 見人就打<br />\n一個唔好彩被佢打到 真係要住成個月醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哩刻放佢走 佢轉頭打第二個㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你以為你救緊人？其實你係害緊你的手足啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺哩個社會 黑警同法律已經制裁唔到佢地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果義士都唔做嘢<br />\n你覺得有咩人先可以令佢地得到應有嘅懲罰呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">四 胡亂起火的人</span></strong><br />\n火之所以危險 唔只係因為佢熱<br />\n更加係因為佢好難控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似尖沙咀咁 燒燒吓無啦啦有個小爆炸<br />\n如果個爆炸係喺路障果到發生 燒到自己人點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要啲火係會驚動到真・消防嚟救熄 增加佢地嘅工作量<br />\n所以大家喺點火之前 記得諗吓佢有冇實質作用（你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n如果你做嘅嘢係有意義、有功用 而又唔會傷害到<span style=\"color: red;\">自己人</span>嘅話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>相信你做咩都唔會有人阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五 極度膽小的前線</span></strong><br />\n如果你咁容易驚 點解唔留喺中線、後線呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好多時候 得幾隻速龍埋嚟<br />\n又或者根本連條狗毛都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前排嘅人就好驚咁向後跑<br />\n連帶後面啲人都跟住跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做成不必要嘅混亂 影響軍心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果你咁易驚 不如試吓其他崗位<br />\n可能有更大嘅作為都唔定呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">六 唔識判斷時勢的勇武</span></strong><br />\n出嚟同黑警對峙唔係為咗被人拉啊<br />\n而係要比壓力佢地同埋政府啊<br />\n如果你被人拉咗 我地又點會比到壓力佢地呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做得勇武 掟得雞蛋 你就要識判斷時勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要知道你可以衝到幾前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要知道啲狗幾時會放屁 咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你判斷錯咗 咁就被人拉㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日話be water be water <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果你唔知個風吹邊面 又點樣若水呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">七 作假標題開po嘅人</span></strong><br />\n其實你開po 都係想表達你嘅所思所想姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗令多啲人睇你個po 為咗多啲留言<br />\n而作個同你嘅內文不符嘅假標題<br />\n其實係表達唔到你真正想講嘅嘢㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更甚嘅係 當大家都出咗去嘅時候<br />\n真係唔會有時間禁入去睇你嘅長篇大論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能只係會掃吓熱門嘅標題<br />\n略略知道各個地方發生咩事 睇吓邊到需要支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>你個假標題係有機會做成混亂㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知唔知</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有啲方法可能係以前work 而家唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但亦都可能調返轉 以前唔work 而家work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯獨一樣嘢 係一直無變嘅<br />\n就係我地出嚟嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">最終目的</span></strong>啊<br />\n咁多位手足 試下花少少時間諗清楚<br />\n我地做嘅每一樣嘢 係為咗啲乜 好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對準腐敗政權 實現五大訴求<br />\n不割𥱊 不篤灰 不分化 不被捕</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話：<br />\n黑警想盡辦法令記者影唔到相 成件事會對抗爭運動好不利<br />\n攝影最基本嘅條件係光<br />\n本身街燈啲光已經唔適合影相 熄埋街燈就仲絕<br />\n各位手足真係要諗辦法搞搞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"d9d8bc91eed4f310f659fa5b845925dd2da2e410","tid":1419071,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:36:44.000Z","msg":"有人提過，唔想放棄黎個可能性。。。。"},{"pid":"d4160fc219568112ed1d0c6be5966e0f503c7c38","tid":1419071,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:38:45.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n幫你share左去其他post"},{"pid":"384e217c0361eaa70c5ae846a99cf551c25922f6","tid":1419071,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:40:45.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c88936d42d1d99078e685966d463a61264cf50","tid":1419071,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575fa956b33472c0099ccb8f2817092c2ca32f1f","tid":1419071,"uid":9435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:44:59.000Z","msg":"泛民做野未呀"},{"pid":"b086e2b52bdabed4be07cc3c2a2e12a887cf8793","tid":1419071,"uid":143183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec8ed18731f9d8cab859ac3a58b7e85dba6ea1e","tid":1419071,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:46:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7bcf83af85869baa442f87ea76992b9953c74cc","tid":1419071,"uid":143183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:47:12.000Z","msg":"呢個堅有用 <br />\n推俾泛民睇"},{"pid":"6b316f1bd435feeeaaafdf9bdd9fcbcacde87748","tid":1419071,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:49:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"815cb1cd6a9e58c1522a3a7858c0248c152a5b45","tid":1419071,"uid":235124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:50:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8eb482837c5b680d410108b9ca01a2f59161ed81","tid":1419071,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:52:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"654d5f966ee121ec0a0f22f90f4506cc9f435d89","tid":1419071,"uid":252222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:54:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"395e192141d6542c29456ec5cf5264274e33cfe5","tid":1419071,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:57:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b372d2060bca042cce0ad027f7c0a912fb03c95","tid":1419071,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:58:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f1862f106fff45ae8522207c995fc74b3f61bdd","tid":1419071,"uid":8017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:59:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ded343cddbb52a4873209ce42a09fb424d47cfdc","tid":1419071,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:02:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69316044fa20a3ffdb610f728a325c